      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "**Module Title: Global Dynamics – Building a Respectful Workplace**\n\n**Introduction:**\nWelcome to our global team! Our success relies on a culture of **respect** that bridges every time zone and background. This guide ensures you understand how to navigate office dynamics with clarity and empathy.\n\n**Section 1: Setting Healthy Boundaries**\n*   **Do:** Clearly communicate your availability and personal time to colleagues.\n*   **Don't:** Over-share private details or expect immediate responses to non-urgent messages.\n*   **Scenario:** If a colleague asks for your personal phone number, politely decline and suggest using the company directory instead. This protects your **boundaries** while maintaining a professional relationship.\n\n**Section 2: Demonstrating Professionalism**\n*   **Do:** Use clear, concise language in emails and video calls.\n*   **Don't:** Use slang, emojis, or informal tone in formal communications.\n*   **Scenario:** When discussing a sensitive project update, choose neutral language to avoid misinterpretation across cultures. This ensures your **professionalism** remains consistent everywhere.\n\n**Section 3: Quick Reference Checklist**\n*   Always ask before sharing sensitive information (**boundaries**).",
      "source": "target",
